Title: Designates portion of the state highway system as the "Detective Brian C. Mulkeen Memorial Bridge"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the town of Woodbury, county of Orange, as the "Detective Brian C. Mulkeen Memorial Bridge".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Detective Brian C. Mulkeen Memorial Bridge"
